 <li><p><strong>Extra Striker:</strong> After an attack and on Trigger 6,
 you can attack again, but only one extra attack can be performed this
 way.</p></li>
 <li><p><strong>Quick Striker (Requires ‘Extra Striker’):</strong> Gain a
 permanent additional attacking action per turn. You may also gain the
 bonus attacking action from Extra Striker.</p></li>
